 o la renuncia a un sueño. La terapia ofrece el espacio seguro para desahogar el dolor sin ser juzgado."}]]}]]}],["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/sintomas/duelo-y-perdidas-significativas","className":"w-full sm:w-auto shrink-0 inline-flex justify-center items-center gap-2 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white font-bold text-xs px-5 py-3 rounded-xl transition mt-4 sm:mt-0 shadow-sm shadow-teal-500/5","children":[["$","svg",null,{"stroke":"currentColor","fill":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"0","viewBox":"0 0 512 512","children":["$undefined",[["$","path","0",{"d":"M256 8C119.043 8 8 119.083 8 256c0 136.997 111.043 248 248 248s248-111.003 248-248C504 119.083 392.957 8 256 8zm0 110c23.196 0 42 18.804 42 42s-18.804 42-42 42-42-18.804-42-42 18.804-42 42-42zm56 254c0 6.627-5.373 12-12 12h-88c-6.627 0-12-5.373-12-12v-24c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h12v-64h-12c-6.627 0-12-5.373-12-12v-24c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h64c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v100h12c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v24z","children":[]}]]],"style":{},"height":12,"width":12,"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"}]," Analizar Caso"]}]]}]}]
